<!-- Refund Policy -->
<div style="background:var(--color-bg-alt);padding:var(--sp-16) 0 var(--sp-8);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section__eyebrow" style="display:block;text-align:left;margin-bottom:var(--sp-3)">Legal</span>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:var(--sp-4)">Refund Policy</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="policy-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="policy-content animate-on-scroll" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto">
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 15, 2026</p>

      <div class="policy-callout" style="margin-bottom:var(--sp-8)"><p>🛡️ Our Promise: We stand behind every product we sell. If you're not completely satisfied, we'll make it right.</p></div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>30-Day Return Policy</h2>
        <p>We offer a <strong>30-day return window</strong> from the date of delivery. Items must be in their original, unused condition with all original packaging, accessories, and documentation.</p>
        <h3>Eligible Returns:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Unused items in original packaging</li>
          <li>Items returned within 30 days of delivery</li>
          <li>Items with original tags and documentation</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Non-Returnable Items:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Items marked "Final Sale"</li>
          <li>Items showing signs of use or installation</li>
          <li>Items without original packaging</li>
          <li>Gift cards</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Refund Process</h2>
        <p>To initiate a return and refund:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Email <a href="mailto:hello@desknet.co">hello@desknet.co</a> with your order number and return reason</li>
          <li>We'll send a prepaid return shipping label within 24 hours</li>
          <li>Pack items securely and drop off at any carrier location</li>
          <li>Once received and inspected (1–3 business days), your refund will be processed</li>
          <li>Refunds appear on your original payment method within 3–10 business days</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Damaged or Defective Items</h2>
        <p>If you receive a damaged or defective item, contact us within 48 hours with photos and we will send a replacement or issue a full refund at no additional cost to you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Late or Missing Refunds</h2>
        <p>If you haven't received your refund after 10 business days, please first check your bank account, then contact your credit card company (it may take time before your refund is officially posted), and then contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@desknet.co">hello@desknet.co</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Refund Policy",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
